content: How do I set up notifications for specific Discord channels, e.g., texting-campaigns when a new campaign drops.

Hi Don, I have a video that shows how to manage your channels. You can also manage notifications on each channel by right clicking on the channel name and picking notifications from the menu, you can manage server-wide notifications same way by clicking on Team Harris-Walz top-left of your screen and choosing notifications from the menu (these instructions are for desktop) the same works on mobile.https://youtu.be/MmPpDMbRG0c
